Interface IProjectRepository

All Superinterfaces:
IRepository<Project,Integer>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CSVProjectRepository
public interface IProjectRepository extends IRepository<Project,Integer>
Repository interface for Project entities. Follows Interface Segregation Principle by extending the generic repository and adding project-specific operations.
